《坦克女郎》的原声带唱片由[[科特妮·洛芙|科特妮·洛芙]]编曲<ref name="ew">{{cite web | archivedate = 2015-11-18 | title = Tank Girl review | last = Gleiberman | first = Owen | date = 1995-04-14 | work = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151118174118/http://www.ew.com/article/1995/04/14/tank-girl | accessdate = 2015-11-24 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.ew.com/article/1995/04/14/tank-girl }}</ref><ref name="Barcella-2012">{{cite book | page = 130 | last = Barcella | first = Laura | date = 2012-07-24 | title = The End: 50 Apocalyptic Visions From Pop Culture That You Should Know About ... Before It's Too Late | accessdate = 2015-11-23 | publisher = Zest Books | isbn = 978-0-9827322-5-0 | url = https://books.google.com.au/books?id=3N43BP2jqlEC&pg=PA130#v=onepage&q&f=false | archive-date = 2015-11-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151125025447/https://books.google.com.au/books?id=3N43BP2jqlEC&pg=PA130#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。原创配乐则是格里莫·瑞维尔（{{lang|en|Graeme Revell}}）谱曲<ref name="brash" />。歌曲《{{lang|en|Drown Soda}}》由洛芙的[[洞穴乐队|洞穴乐队]]演出。[[邪教合唱团|邪教合唱团]]的[[格雷格·格拉芬|格雷格·格拉芬]]（{{lang|en|Greg Graffin}}）原订同[[琼·杰特|琼·杰特]]一起表演二重唱《{{lang|en|Let's Do It, Let's Fall in Love}}》，但之后因合同条款限制而被[[代替乐队|代替乐队]]的[[保罗·韦斯特伯格|保罗·韦斯特伯格]]（{{lang|en|Paul Westerberg}}）取代。[[Devo乐队|Devo乐队]]是原著漫画的粉丝，他们为本片专门录制了歌曲《{{lang|en|Girl U Want}}》的新版本。<ref name="rosen">{{cite journal | last = Rosen | first = Craig | date = 1995-03-25 | title = 'Tank Girl' Set shoots From Hip | archivedate = 2017-12-24 | journal = [[告示牌_(杂志)|Billboard]] | deadurl = no | url = https://books.google.com.au/books?id=7AsEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA10#v=onepage&q&f=false | volume = 107 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171224042414/https://books.google.com.au/books?id=7AsEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA10#v=onepage&q&f=false | issue = 12 | pages = 10, 44 | accessdate = 2015-11-25 }}</ref>原声带中还收录有比约克的歌曲《{{lang|en|[[Army_of_Me_(比约克歌曲)|Army of Me]]}}》，这首歌之后还作为单曲发行。由于电影在票房上失利，比约克及其唱片公司都决定不在单曲的音乐视频中采用电影镜头。<ref name="declined">{{cite journal | last = Atwood | first = Brett | date = 1995-05-13 | title = Elektra's Bjork Putting A Love Letter in The 'Post' | journal = Billboard | volume = 107 | issue = 19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171224101157/https://books.google.com.au/books?id=vAsEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA17#v=onepage&q&f=false | pages = 17–18 | url = https://books.google.com.au/books?id=vAsEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA17#v=onepage&q&f=false | accessdate = 2015-11-23 | archivedate = 2017-12-24 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

洛芙主动同[[斯科特·韦兰德|斯科特·韦兰德]]（{{lang|en|Scott Weiland}}）取得联系，请他为电影原声带贡献一曲，韦兰德作为副业参与的壮丽杂种乐队（{{lang|en|The Magnificent Bastards}}）于是特别录制了歌曲《知更鸟女孩》（{{lang|en|''Mockingbird Girl''}}）<ref>{{cite journal | last = Azzerad | first = Michael | date = 1995-08 | title = Peace, Love, and Understanding | url = https://books.google.com.au/books?id=iqjQUZoqfawC&pg=PA58#v=onepage&q&f=false | journal = Spin | page = 57 | volume = 11 | issue = 5 | accessdate = 2015-11-23 | archivedate = 2017-12-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171224101203/https://books.google.com.au/books?id=iqjQUZoqfawC&pg=PA58#v=onepage&q&f=false }}</ref>。单面唱片的封面是某动画人物（看起来很像坦克妹）的躯干和大腿，还包含电影原声带唱片中的歌曲《{{lang|en|Ripper Sole}}》和《{{lang|en|Girl U Want}}》。歌曲在美国[[主流摇滚排行榜|主流摇滚排行榜]]上最高排到第27位，在[[另类歌曲排行榜|现代摇滚曲目]]排行榜上则最高升至第12位。<ref name="billboard">{{cite web |publisher=AllMusic |accessdate=2015-11-25 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/tank-girl-mw0000644032/awards |title=Tank Girl Awards |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120708065216/http://www.allmusic.com/album/tank-girl-mw0000644032/awards |archivedate=2012-07-08 }}</ref>电影中还出现[[贝奥武夫乐队|贝奥-{武}-夫乐队]]的歌曲《2分》（{{lang|en|''2￠''}}），塔拉蕾期望能说服[[Restless唱片|Restless唱片]]将这首歌也收入原声带，但公司没有接受她的建议。歌曲的音乐视频也由塔拉蕾导演，其中包含电影中的真人和动画片段。<ref>{{cite journal | date = 1995-04-08 | title = Tank Attack | archivedate = 2017-12-24 | deadurl = no | journal = Billboard | volume = 107 | url = https://books.google.com.au/books?id=6AsEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA53#v=onepage&q&f=false | issue = 14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171224101159/https://books.google.com.au/books?id=6AsEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA53#v=onepage&q&f=false | pages = 53 | accessdate = 2015-11-23 | author1 = Nielsen Business Media | first1 = Inc }}</ref>

电影的原声带唱片于1995年3月28日由[[华纳兄弟唱片公司|华纳兄弟]]和埃里克特拉唱片公司发布，在[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]中最高冲至第72名<ref name="billboard" />。1周后，《[[纽约_(杂志)|纽约]]》（{{lang|en|''New York''}}）杂志发文称，这张唱片的关注度比电影本身还高<ref>{{cite journal | date = 1995-04-03 | title = Tank Girl | url = https://books.google.com.au/books?id=7OQCAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA86#v=onepage&q&f=false | journal = New York | volume = 28 | issue = 14 | page = 86 | accessdate = 2015-11-23 | author1 = New York Media | first1 = LLC | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308235634/https://books.google.com.au/books?id=7OQCAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA86#v=onepage&q&f=false | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。不过，[[淘儿唱片|淘儿唱片]]的罗恩·汉考克（{{lang|en|Ron Hancock}}）称唱片销量不佳，认为这主要是因为电影在商业上的失败<ref name="declined" />。[[欧文·格雷伯曼|欧文·格雷伯曼]]（{{lang|en|Owen Gleiberman}}）给予原声带好评<ref name="ew" />，劳拉·巴塞拉（{{lang|en|Laura Barcella}}）在著作《结局》（{{lang|en|''The End''}}）中也有同样看法，称其为“90年代的女性摇滚”<ref name="Barcella-2012" />。{{lang|en|[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]}}网站的斯蒂芬·托马斯·厄尔温（{{lang|en|Stephen Thomas Erlewine}}）则表示唱片“比电影强太多了”，他给予的评分为3星（最高5星）<ref>{{cite web | publisher = AllMusic | accessdate = 2015-11-25 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/tank-girl-mw0000644032 | last = Erlewine | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151020212651/http://www.allmusic.com/album/tank-girl-mw0000644032 | archivedate = 2015-10-20 | title = Original Soundtrack: Tank Girl | first = Stephen Thoma }}</ref>。

