== 发行 ==

=== 首映式和票房成绩 ===
[[File:Malcolm_McDowell_Cannes_2011.jpg|thumb]]（摄于2011年）在片中扮演大反派克斯里]]
1995年3月30日，《坦克女郎》的首映式在[[中国戏院|曼恩中国戏院]]举行，约有1500人出席，其中包括塔拉蕾、佩蒂、艾斯-{{lang|en|T}}、麦克道威尔、沃茨和参加演出的另外多名演员。一同出席的还包括[[瑞贝卡·德·莫妮|瑞贝卡·德·莫妮]]、[[劳伦·汤姆|劳伦·汤姆]]（{{lang|en|Lauren Tom}}）、[[布兰登·费舍|布兰登·费舍]]和[[贾森·西蒙斯|贾森·西蒙斯]]（{{lang|en|Jason Simmons}}）。身着片中水威力公司服装的男性工作人员在现场发放矿泉水，还有身穿液态银俱乐部服饰的女性发放3色棒棒糖、[[香烟糖|香烟糖]]和“坦克女郎”糖果项链。另外还有约400人在首映式后前往[[好莱坞罗斯福酒店|好莱坞罗斯福酒店]]，出席正式的余兴聚会。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1995-04-03/news/ls-50404_1_tank-girl | title = RSVP : Tanked Up at Moocher's Paradise | archivedate = 2015-05-10 | last = Ehran | first = Mark | date = 1995-04-03 | work = [[洛杉矶时报|Los Angeles Times]] | accessdate = 2015-11-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150510093136/http://articles.latimes.com/1995-04-03/news/ls-50404_1_tank-girl }}</ref>电影于次日开始在美国各地院线上映<ref name="mojo" />。

《坦克女郎》在全美1341家电影院上映，第一个周末共计进账201万8183美元<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2015-06-26 |title=Tank Girl (R) |url=http://pro.boxoffice.com/statistics/movies/tank-girl-1995 |work=BOXOFFICE |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626122956/http://pro.boxoffice.com/statistics/movies/tank-girl-1995 |accessdate=2015-11-25 }}</ref>，首周票房则为268万4430美元。但是，电影上映两周时的票房一共只有366万8762美元，最终在美国的总收入为406万4495美元<ref name="mojo" />。影片在国际市场的发行收入约为200万美元<ref name="international" />，相比之下，电影的制作预算为2500万美元<ref name="mojo" />。

=== 专业评价 ===
[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]网站收集有37篇针对《坦克女郎》的评论文章，其中只有14篇给出“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”仅38%，平均评分4.9（最高10分）。网站的共识评价这样写道：“《坦克女郎》虽然标新立异，但并没有什么特别巧妙或引人入胜之处，剧本中的俏皮话虽多，但都没有真正的诚意。”<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2015-10-15 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tank_girl/ | title = Tank Girl | publisher = [[烂番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate = 2015-11-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151015201430/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tank_girl/ }}</ref>[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]的拉马尔·哈菲尔达森（{{lang|en|Lamar Hafildason}}）对影片的评分只有1星（最高5星），称：“遗憾的是，英国广播公司不会为只有一个词的评论支付稿酬，要是会的话，这篇评论就会简短得多：‘烦人’”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2001/06/26/tank_girl_1995_review.shtml |accessdate=2015-11-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091227034412/http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2001/06/26/tank_girl_1995_review.shtml |deadurl=no |archivedate=2009-12-27 |title=Tank Girl (1995) |last=Haflidason |first=Almar |date=2001-06-26 |publisher=BBC }}</ref>。2001年，[[CL公司|CL公司]]的马特·布伦森（{{lang|en|Matt Brunson}}）给予本片1星半（最高4星）的评级，认为电影的摇滚配乐表现尚佳，还能对娜奥米·沃茨出道早期的表演有惊鸿一瞥，但这都不足以挽救这部电影在票房上惨败收场<ref>{{cite web | date = 2001-06-26 | publisher = BBC | last = Brunson | accessdate = 2015-11-25 | deadurl = no | url = http://clclt.com/charlotte/all-the-presidents-men-assault-on-precinct-13-red-2-among-new-home-entertainment-titles/Content?oid=3271457 | title = All the President's Men, Assault on Precinct 13, Red 2 among new home entertainment titles | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150909161904/http://clclt.com/charlotte/all-the-presidents-men-assault-on-precinct-13-red-2-among-new-home-entertainment-titles/Content?oid=3271457 | archivedate = 2015-09-09 | first = Matt }}</ref>。[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]给予《坦克女郎》的评分为2星（最高4星）。在他看来，电影的抱负和精力值得称道，但其中打动人心的力量却无法持续，并且过不了多久，电影中那种狂躁的能量就开始令人感到厌烦<ref>{{cite web | work = [[芝加哥太阳报|Chicago Sun-Times]] | deadurl = no | url = http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/tank-girl-1995 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150919060515/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/tank-girl-1995 | archivedate = 2015-09-19 | title = Tank Girl review | last = Ebert | first = Roger | date = 1995-03-31 | accessdate = 2015-11-25 }}</ref>。

欧文·格雷伯曼对本片的评级为{{lang|en|C–}}，认为佩蒂的演出是这部“业余”电影中唯一的亮点<ref name="ew" />。[[乔纳森·罗森鲍姆|乔纳森·罗森鲍姆]]（{{lang|en|Jonathan Rosenbaum}}）和[[珍妮特·马斯林|珍妮特·马斯林]]（{{lang|en|Janet Maslin}}）对电影有偏向正面的评价，罗森鲍姆宣称：“除非你是还没到青春期并且[[厌女症|讨厌女孩]]的男孩，否则你就会觉得这部电影要比《[[永远的蝙蝠侠|永远的蝙蝠侠]]》有意思得多”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/tank-girl/Film?oid=1068593 | archivedate = 2015-07-15 | title = Tank Girl | last = Rosenbaum | first = Jonathan | work = Chicago Reader | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150715091843/http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/tank-girl/Film?oid=1068593 | accessdate = 2015-07-15 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。马期林则称赞佩蒂的演出为坦克妹一角增色不少，在原本颇显浮躁的角色中加入更多耐人寻味的东西<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=990CE3DB123CF932A05750C0A963958260 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150721175632/http://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=990CE3DB123CF932A05750C0A963958260 | archivedate = 2015-07-21 | title = Tank Girl (1995) | last = Maslin | first = Janet | date = 1995-03-31 | work = The New York Times | accessdate = 2015-11-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。伦纳德·克拉迪（{{lang|en|Leonard Klady}}）在《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》杂志发文，称电影空有引人入胜的节奏，但却缺乏动人的故事情节；佩蒂扮演的坦克妹虽有胆识，但还不足以成为世界末日之后的女英雄<ref>{{cite journal | url = http://variety.com/1995/film/reviews/tank-girl-2-1200440887/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150703011001/http://variety.com/1995/film/reviews/tank-girl-2-1200440887/ | archivedate = 2015-07-03 | title = Review: 'Tank Girl' | last = Klady | first = Leonard | date = 1995-03-29 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2015-11-25 | journal =  | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

