面对逐渐下滑的订阅率，《最后期限》杂志在1994至1995年间多次使用坦克妹作为封面人物，希望改编电影的上映能为杂志销量带来突破。汤姆·阿斯特之后表示，电影的发行“很有帮助，但也有些得不偿失，（漫画）失去部分邪典爱好者（支持）的同时，也没得到任何主流媒体青眼相看。”<ref name="Shirley-2005">{{cite book | last = Shirley | first = Ian | date = 2005-08-22 | title = Can Rock & Roll Save The World?: An Illustrated History of Music And Comics | url = https://books.google.com.au/books?id=rGhccTlnwSUC&pg=PA255#v=onepage&q&f=false | publisher = SAF publishing | accessdate = 2015-11-23 | isbn = 978-0-946719-80-8 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160309060629/https://books.google.com.au/books?id=rGhccTlnwSUC&pg=PA255#v=onepage&q&f=false | archivedate = 2016-03-09 | deadurl = no }}</ref>{{rp|255}}杂志于1995年下半年停刊<ref name="Shirley-2005" />{{rp|257}}。阿兰·马丁和杰米·休莱特此后一直对这部电影的创作持负面态度，称参与本片制作是他们“不堪回首的痛苦往事”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sci-fi-online.com/Interview/02-11-22_AlanMartin.htm | accessdate = 2015-11-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150927171245/http://sci-fi-online.com/Interview/02-11-22_AlanMartin.htm | archivedate = 2015-09-27 | title = Alan Martin on Tank Girl | work = sci-fi online }}</ref>。根据休莱特的回忆：“剧本不怎么样”，“我和阿兰反复改写，加入《[[格兰其山|格兰其山]]》（{{lang|en|''Grange Hill''}}）和[[班尼·希尔|班尼·希尔]]的喜剧元素，但他们显然都不明白。他们漏拍了大概10场重要戏码，以至于我们只能用动画加进去……这样的经历让人感觉糟透了”<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2011-07-28 |title=Jamie Hewlett interview |last=Fairs |url=http://www.iconeye.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&catid=310:icon%20036&id=2494:jamie-hewlett--icon-036--june-2006 |first=Marcus |date=2006-06 |work=Icon Magazine |accessdate=2011-07-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110728064040/http://www.iconeye.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&catid=310%3Aicon%20036&id=2494%3Ajamie-hewlett--icon-036--june-2006 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。塔拉蕾则批评制片商对电影包括剧情在内的多个方面干涉太多<ref name="stomp" /><ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121224071918/http://www.twisted.org.uk/tg/movie.cut.html |url=http://www.twisted.org.uk/tg/movie.cut.html |title=Tank Girl Movie: The Outtakes |last1=Talalay |first1=Rachel |last2=Rosenberg |first2=Bob |work=Tank Girl |accessdate=2015-11-26 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2012-12-24 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | accessdate = 2012-03-08 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-03-08 | url = http://nightmareonelmstreetfilms.com/nightmareinterviewsrachel.html | title = A Q&A with Rachel Talalay | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120308102852/http://nightmareonelmstreetfilms.com/nightmareinterviewsrachel.html | date = 2005-03-25 | work = Nightmare on Elm Street Companion }}</ref>。据她所说，当时她已经同马丁和休莱特在许多方向达成共识，但制片公司之后主导了电影的后期剪辑，剪掉了大量内容，对此她没有控制权<ref name="commentary" />。1995年，[[彼得·米利根|彼得·米利根]]（{{lang|en|Peter Milligan}}）创作的改编漫画面世<ref>{{cite book | archivedate = 2015-07-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150723000700/https://openlibrary.org/books/OL540196M/Tank_girl | deadurl = no | url = https://openlibrary.org/books/OL540196M/Tank_girl | title = Tank girl | work = Open Library | accessdate = 2015-11-26 | isbn = 1563892197 | lccn = 96119231 }}</ref>，[[马丁·米拉尔|马丁·米拉尔]]（{{lang|en|Martin Millar}}）根据电影改编创作的小说于1996年发行<ref>{{cite book | url = https://openlibrary.org/books/OL7351212M/Tank_Girl | isbn = 9780140248760 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150722221949/https://openlibrary.org/books/OL7351212M/Tank_Girl | oclc = 32892033 | archivedate = 2015-07-22 | title = Tank Girl: Novelisation | work = Open Library | accessdate = 2015-11-26 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

虽然在商业和评论上都是失败之作，但《坦克女郎》却得到[[邪典电影|邪典]]受众的追捧<ref name="redemption">{{cite news | date = 2014-03-06 | accessdate = 2015-11-26 | last = Volmers | first = Eric | work = Calgary Herald | deadurl = no | url = http://calgaryherald.com/entertainment/the-blu-ray-redemption-of-tank-girl-director-rachel-talalay-talks-about-her-1995-cult-films-handsome-rebirth-on-dvd | archivedate = 2015-02-09 | title = The blu-ray redemption of Tank Girl: Director Rachel Talalay talks about her 1995 cult film's handsome rebirth on DVD | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150209180815/http://calgaryherald.com/entertainment/the-blu-ray-redemption-of-tank-girl-director-rachel-talalay-talks-about-her-1995-cult-films-handsome-rebirth-on-dvd }}</ref><ref name="Barcella-2012" /><ref name=Mathijs-Mendik-2007>{{cite book |last1=Mathijs |first1=Ernest |last2=Mendik |first2=Xavier |date=2007-12-01 |title=The Cult Film Reader |accessdate=2015-11-23 |publisher=Open University Press |isbn=978-0-335-21923-0 |page=9 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dWX4AAAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=The+Cult+Film+Reader+ernerst&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=tank%20girl&f=false |archivedate=2016-07-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729034317/https://books.google.com/books?id=dWX4AAAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=The+Cult+Film+Reader+ernerst&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=tank%20girl&f=false }}</ref>。佩蒂扮演的坦克妹至今仍是{{lang|en|[[Cosplay|Cosplay]]}}活动中的热门人物<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | url = http://screencrush.com/cosplay-of-the-day-tank-girl/ | title = Cosplay of the Day: Don't Mess With Tank Girl Unless You Want to Get Bombed | last = Hayes | first1 = Britt | date = 2013-02-22 | work = Screen Crush | accessdate = 2015-11-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151015202217/http://screencrush.com/cosplay-of-the-day-tank-girl/ | archivedate = 2015-10-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://uproxx.com/gammasquad/2015/03/tank-girl-cosplay-of-the-week/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151011220211/http://uproxx.com/gammasquad/2015/03/tank-girl-cosplay-of-the-week/ | archivedate = 2015-10-11 | title = Tank Girl Anniversary Edition of the Funny, Sexy, And Awesome Cosplay of the Week | last = Panda | first1 = Robo | date = 2015-03-27 | work = Uproxxx | accessdate = 2015-11-26 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[艾薇儿·拉维尼|艾薇儿·拉维尼]]2013年歌曲《[[摇滚万岁|摇滚万岁]]》的音乐视频受到本片的显著影响<ref name="radio.com">{{cite news | last = E. Smith | first = Courtney | title = Avril Lavigne Pays Homage To 'Tank Girl' With 'Rock N Roll' Video | archivedate = 2015-10-15 | deadurl = yes | url = http://radio.com/2013/08/20/avril-lavigne-pays-homage-to-tank-girl-with-rock-n-roll-video/ | accessdate = 2015-11-26 | publisher = Radio.com | date = 2013-08-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151015202446/http://radio.com/2013/08/20/avril-lavigne-pays-homage-to-tank-girl-with-rock-n-roll-video/ }}</ref>。2013年发行的电影蓝光影碟中收录有针对佩蒂的采访，面对电影为何还能引起影迷共鸣的问题她回答：“《坦克女郎》为何会如此精彩，何以会令他人如此流连忘返，这样的问题并没有标准答案……这部电影独一无二、开拓创新而且领先于它的时代，我很高兴自己能够参与其中，并且我也会永远钟爱于她”<ref>{{cite AV media | people = Lori Petty | year = 2013 | title = Baseballs, Tanks and Bad Tattoos: An interview with Actress Lori Petty | medium = Blu-ray featurette}}</ref>。[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]的卢克·巴克马斯特（{{lang|en|Luke Buckmaster}}）于2015年将本片列入“十部最古怪的超级英雄电影”，他在评价中称：“从最好的角度来说，导演瑞秋·塔拉蕾捕捉到一种招摇的蒸汽朋克氛围，事实证明，这种氛围虽然古怪，但却容易令人上瘾”<ref>{{cite web | publisher = BBC | accessdate = 2015-11-26 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.bbc.com/culture/story/20150811-the-10-weirdest-superhero-films | first = Luke | last = Buckmaster | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151024034816/http://www.bbc.com/culture/story/20150811-the-10-weirdest-superhero-films | archivedate = 2015-10-24 | title = The 10 weirdest superhero films | date = 2015-08-11 }}</ref>。

2019年9月，據報導，女演員[[瑪歌·羅比|瑪歌·羅比]]的製片公司[[LuckyChap娛樂|LuckyChap娛樂]]從米高梅手中取得了《坦克女郎》的電影版權，正在籌備一部重啟作<ref>{{cite web |url=http://collider.com/margot-robbie-tank-girl-director-miles-joris-peyrafitte/ |title=Exclusive: Margot Robbie’s ‘Tank Girl’ Movie Lands Director Miles Joris-Peyrafitte |last=Sneider |first=Jeff |date=2019-09-10 |accessdate=2019-09-14 |work=[[Collider_(網站)|Collider]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912035827/http://collider.com/margot-robbie-tank-girl-director-miles-joris-peyrafitte/ |archivedate=2019-09-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。
